{
  "stem": "1895.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 430.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, some of the boys that were with me-- we were about 100 boys in that group-- encountered their relatives, their mothers, their fathers, being taken out the other way, towards the trains.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so they-- you know, they- they tried to communicate with them, tried-- one of them tried to jump out and embrace them and say goodbye to them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he got shot immediately, as well as his parents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw sights of dozens of baby carriages with babies in them dead, killed, shot, mothers holding on to parts of the carriages in a deadly grip.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember seeing one elderly woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She was sitting on a suitcase in a pool of blood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was bleeding all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she wasn't dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was cursing God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she was pleading for someone to come and kill her, because she was in tremendous pain.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for about a half hour, the time it took for us-- and we were trotting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were not walking, because the guard told us to keep our heads down and trot.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those were Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We witnessed all of these things as we passed by.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the field probably held [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] hundreds of dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the SS was in control.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they had-- they had guards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had young guards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember-- it's a good question you asked, because I want to bring that out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As we passed the columns that were on their way to the trains, we also passed their guards that were guarding the columns.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what struck me at the time was the fresh-faced, clean-looking, young boys that were guarding these columns.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
